Myra De Groot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Myra_De_Groot 0 Myra Tania De Groot (4 July 1937 – 4 April 1988) was a British-born theatre and television actress and agent. She performed in the United Kingdom, New Zealand and Australia. Myra_Tania_De_Groot ( 4_July_1937 – 4_April_1988 ) was a_British-born_theatre_and_television_actress_and_agent .
